endingSummaries.summaryText: You lived a great life. There were good days and bad days, but you always managed to see the brighter side of every situation and lived your best life. How corny.
This was a good life. There were some less enjoyable time, but you still managed well. But you secretly resent those who had a better time than you...
An above average existance. Nothing major to celebrate and nothing major to mourn. You could have been so much more... if only you had applied yourself.
What a disappointment. You had SUCH potential!
